dc.title: House of Representatives Live Video: HouseLive.gov
dc.description: Follow the work of the U.S. House of Representatives straight from the Floor - live or anytime from your computer or mobile device - on HouseLive.gov. Watch or download video of Floor proceedings dating back to the 111th Congress through the House's on-demand service.
